  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下教育内容分发系统的数据流。核心场景是：外部系统通过API获取设备列表，但中间需要经过多层过滤和权限校验。起点我称之为Education_ContentCDN，它扮演APIClient的角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，ContentCDN作为客户端发起请求。那这个请求首先到达哪里？是直连数据库还是有专门的接入层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "请求会先发送到Education_LMS_Portal，这个组件我们叫它DeviceController，负责接收和路由。ContentCDN会sends filter input给这个Portal。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "sends filter input"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这条主链路画出来：ContentCDN指向LMS Portal，标注为发送过滤条件。接下来Portal内部怎么处理这个请求？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "sends filter input"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Portal本身不直接查数据，它需要用到DeviceFilterInput这个结构来解析过滤条件——注意这个过滤输入也是定义在Education_LMS_Portal内部的。然后Portal会把实际的数据获取工作delegate出去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "delegates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "delegates的目标是谁？另外过滤输入和Portal是同一个节点还是分开的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "过滤输入是Portal内部使用的，所以是uses关系。delegates的目标是Education_GradeSync，我们叫它DeviceDataFetcher，专门负责成绩相关的数据聚合。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "uses",
        "delegates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：Portal uses DeviceFilterInput，同时delegates到GradeSync。那GradeSync去哪里拿原始数据？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GradeSync会applies filters到DataSource，这个数据源我们还是用Education_LMS_Portal来表示，因为实际数据存储在Portal的后端。然后GradeSync要把结果returns给Portal。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "applies filters",
        "returns results"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：GradeSync到DataSource是applies filters，GradeSync回Portal是returns results。最后Portal怎么回复最初的ContentCDN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource",
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Portal会responds给APIClient，完成整个闭环。这样从请求发起到数据返回的完整链路就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient",
        "responds"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整个流程已确认：ContentCDN发送过滤条件到LMS Portal，Portal使用内部过滤结构并委托GradeSync处理，GradeSync应用过滤到数据源后返回结果，最终Portal响应ContentCDN。结构完整，没有遗漏。",
      "elements_involved": [
